original_title: What It Means To Be A Woman (If That Means Anything At All)
overview: Whilst getting ready for a night out, Etta and Mitzie get locked in their bathroom. Despite no longer being able to go out, Mitzie continues getting ready, to Etta's confusion. This prompts a conversation between the two women as to their motivations for dressing up, if it's for themselves or for other people.
title: What It Means To Be A Woman (If That Means Anything At All)
